dc_description_s: This line shapefile shows major roads in Kenya. These data were originally produced as a 1:250,000 topographic map by the Geological Survey of Kenya.This data was used in maps throughout Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
